

                          [help consider]
-----------------------=========+=========-----------------------



Usage: consider <target>
Cost: 5 spell points(for those beneath level 5)
      10 spell points(for those above level 5)

 This spell will help you gauge the strength of a player or
creature.  It will tell you the level of armor of the target,
their weapon strength, and how much damage they can take in a
fight.

